  {
    title: "Instant Backend Setup",
    description:
      "Supabase provides all backend services out-of-the-box, including databases, authentication, and real-time capabilities, significantly reducing setup times.",
  },
  {
    title: "Real-time Interactivity",
    description:
      "HTMX allows you to add real-time interactivity to your web pages without writing complex JavaScript, keeping your applications light and fast.",
  },
  {
